skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
As part of your Flash Briefing, include a list of all significant earthquakes worldwide over the past month.

The Big Quake Bot feed is originally sourced from the USGS "Significant Earthquakes, Past Month" feed.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
